TITLE: Merging ERC Token ABIs in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Basic example showing how to merge ERC20 and ERC4626 ABIs using the mergeAbis utility function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ponder-sh/ponder/blob/main/docs/pages/docs/utilities/merge-abis.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { mergeAbis } from "@ponder/utils";
import { erc20Abi, erc4626Abi } from "viem";

const tokenAbi = mergeAbis([erc20Abi, erc4626Abi]);
```

