TITLE: Configuring Telemetry Opt-Out in Ponder
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to disable telemetry in Ponder by setting the PONDER_TELEMETRY_DISABLED environment variable to true in a .env.local file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ponder-sh/ponder/blob/main/docs/pages/0_6/docs/advanced/telemetry.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
PONDER_TELEMETRY_DISABLED = true
```

