TITLE: Running create-ponder with Package Managers
DESCRIPTION: Commands to create a new Ponder project using different package managers (pnpm, yarn, npm)
SOURCE: https://github.com/ponder-sh/ponder/blob/main/docs/pages/0_6/docs/api-reference/create-ponder.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
pnpm create ponder {...options}
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
yarn create ponder {...options}
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm create ponder@latest {...options}
```

